            "inline": true,
            "width": "22.57895720215113px",
            "height": "16.42105978338265px"
          },
          "）。调节电压读数盘相当于调节 上图8-1 中的",
          {
            "nodeId": "SYBZ_Fill_8",
            "width": "50px"
          },
          "（请填写答案序号：1、",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_potentiometer_img_017.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "20.01316661099756px",
            "height": "16.93421790161332px"
          },
          "，2、",
          {
