            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_potentiometer_img_018.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "20.01316661099756px",
            "height": "16.42105978338265px"
          },
          "，3、",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_potentiometer_img_019.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "22.57895720215113px",
            "height": "16.42105978338265px"
          },
          "）。\n具体实验步骤：\n1. 将倍率旋钮从“断”旋到所需的倍率K，其中测量干电池电动势时，应选择×",
          {
